# Playground — `@br-validators/core` integration

## Symptom

Next.js build fails:

```
Module not found: Can't resolve './cnpj.js'
Import trace: ../../packages/br-validators/src/index.ts
```

## Root cause

`tsconfig` `paths` pointed at `packages/br-validators/src/`. Next bundles **source**; core uses Node ESM specifiers (`./cnpj.js`) that exist only in **`dist/`** after `tsup`.

## Fix (required pattern)

| Layer | Config | Target |
|-------|--------|--------|
| IDE / `tsc` | `apps/playground/tsconfig.json` `paths` | `../../packages/br-validators/dist/index.d.ts` and `dist/*.d.ts` |
| Webpack / runtime | `apps/playground/next.config.mjs` `resolve.alias` | `../../packages/br-validators/dist/*.js` |
| Pre-build | `apps/playground/package.json` `prebuild` | `pnpm --filter @br-validators/core build` |

## Agent MUST NOT

- Set `paths` to `packages/br-validators/src/**` in playground.
- Enable `transpilePackages: ['@br-validators/core']` (re-triggers src bundle).
- Add `declare module '@br-validators/core'` shims.

## Verify

```bash
pnpm --filter @br-validators/core build
pnpm --filter @br-validators/playground build
pnpm --filter @br-validators/playground typecheck
```
